{"id":585620,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/05/维权网-安徽省六安市公办教师数百人示威遭警察/","date":"2018-05-28T09:01:55Z","modified":"2018-05-28T10:28:11Z","title":"维权网 | 安徽省六安市公办教师数百人示威遭警察阻击和带离","content":"<p>(维权网信息员姚立法报道) 2018年5月27日上午9时，安徽省六安市所辖的金安区和裕安区等区县的、在职公办教师两百多人(也有老师说有三至四百人)，在接近市政府时，遭到警察的暴力拦截并带走16人(其中裕安区10人、金安区6人)。</p>\n<p>老师们准备好的横幅还没有展开就被警察收走，同时多位老师被多个警察按倒在地上，有一位戴眼睛的男老师、双手臂被四位警察反剪着押上警车，人群中老师们不停呼喊口号。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeM-K8CU0AAvIgY.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-585623\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeM-K8CU0AAvIgY.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"654\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeM-K8CU0AAvIgY.jpg 367w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeM-K8CU0AAvIgY-184x300.jpg 184w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeM-K48VQAAEVO_.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-585624\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeM-K48VQAAEVO_.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeM-K48VQAAEVO_.jpg 384w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeM-K48VQAAEVO_-240x300.jpg 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeM-K49U8AAdx2t.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-585625\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeM-K49U8AAdx2t.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"563\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeM-K49U8AAdx2t.jpg 345w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeM-K49U8AAdx2t-213x300.jpg 213w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeNMb7_VMAA66EL2.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-585627\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeNMb7_VMAA66EL2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"427\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeNMb7_VMAA66EL2.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeNMb7_VMAA66EL2-281x300.jpg 281w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeNMb7_VMAA66EL.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-585626\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeNMb7_VMAA66EL.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeNMb7_VMAA66EL.jpg 480w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeNMb7_VMAA66EL-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>据悉，当局对该市公办老师们计划集体&#8221;讨薪&#8221;维权活动情报已查获。昨天全市各学校校长给老师们打手机，&#8221;劝&#8221;老师们不要参与游行示威活动。</p>\n<p>参加今天游行示威的老师，主要是在农村学校任教的人。</p>\n<p>据六安市的老师对维权网信息员介绍，六安市各行政单位工作人员、市直各学校的老师2016年和2017年两年的一次性绩效工资共计三万六千元，早已打到卡上，但各区县特别是农村学校的老师没有得到这笔该得的钱。</p>\n<p>据悉，冲突中一位受伤女老师送去人民医院还不让住院，后来老师们把她抬去妇幼保健院。</p>\n<p>警察和教师的冲突大约进行了一个小时就结束了。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/725f1802gy1frq8i6z3s1j20rs0rswlf.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-585622\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/725f1802gy1frq8i6z3s1j20rs0rswlf.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/725f1802gy1frq8i6z3s1j20rs0rswlf.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/725f1802gy1frq8i6z3s1j20rs0rswlf-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/725f1802gy1frq8i6z3s1j20rs0rswlf-300x300.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/725f1802gy1frq8i6z3s1j20rs0rswlf-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/725f1802gy1frq8i6z3s1j20rs0rswlf-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,19168,20534],"tags":[19946,9526,34765,10943,8906,9503,16917]}